Robot can serve as a taxi driver. It is more reliable than autonomous vehicles as it comes with a huge array of sensors and a highly sophisticated artificial intelligence.
Robots can help in building and construction of tall buildings and go into areas that would prove dangerous for humans. This would reduce casualties of construction workers.

Robots can work in manufacturing facilities and complete work much more efficient and at a cheaper cost than humans.

Robot can help with advertising and advise people with shopping based on their interests.

Being highly efficient and effective, this robot can replace humans and decrease net expense of the company purchasing it. 
These robots have a one-time cost unlike humans who are paid every year.

Assistance as a personal guide in foreign places</i></p><br>
